    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A type of structural plate glass that is ground to true plane surfaces; used for storefronts, countertops, tiling, and paneling. It is made in many colors in thicknesses from 11/32 to 1 1/2 inches (0.86 to 3.81 cm) or laminated to give different color effects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Un tipo de vidrio plano que se apoya contra superficies verdaderamente planas. Se utiliza en fachadas de tiendas, mesada de mostradores, techos y paneles. Se hace en varios colores, en grosores de 11/32 a 1 1/2 pulgadas (0,86 a 3,81 cm.) o laminado, para dar diferentes efectos de color.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Type vlakglas dat wordt geslepen tot werkelijk gladde oppervlakken. Gebruikt voor winkelpuien, aanrechtbladen, tegels en panelen. Het wordt in vele kleuren gemaakt in dikten van 0,86 tot 3,81 cm of gelamineerd om verschillende kleureffecten te geven.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種平板玻璃，經研磨後具有平坦表面，用於店面、檯面、鋪磚及嵌板。可製成多種顏色，厚度從11/32到1.5英吋（約為0.86至3.81公分）不等，也可以層疊方式創造不同色彩效果。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
